data.title: Bunbury Brewery Co. Perth, Australia. A Pair of Beer Labels for Pale Ale and Stout
data.meta_description: Perth: Sands & McDougall, Ca. 1900. Two lithographed beer labels, one on red paper and printed in red and black, the second on cream paper and printed in black, and both with the brewery's logo. Bottled by H. Sherwood & Co. Esplanade, Perth. 3 1/2 x 2 3/4 Very good condition. Item #22027
